,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:27:39.000Z","msg":"我覺得拜登有可能選到, 但最多只係拖慢對付中共的腳步, 民主國家圍攻或者圍堵中共的策略唔會變.  <br />\n<br />\n依家民主國家日日都感受到威脅, 例如依家聯合國人權理事會選新理事國, 幾個民主大國聯手都完全阻唔到獨裁國家, 冇理由仲未知驚."},{"pid":"950b01c3bbb55c34cb792c4e02e4f946b2f4d54c","tid":2241034,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef97a40a89bf31e7cefe6c22f46fab27c9a7c4a3","tid":2241034,"uid":316612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9c7c354acfe5410ee085ca95317dba065dbd866","tid":2241034,"uid":112581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e26627c56380cae05e720086f4186090b366a6b7","tid":2241034,"uid":316612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"又係大台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"班要民陣帶頭申請不反既200萬人算唔算大台狗？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:25:55.000Z","msg":"跟大台做野唔係問題，好似你呢種非大台即五毛熱狗pr，先係大台狗。你地最叻分化香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:27:46.000Z","msg":"跟大台做野唔係問題<br />\n冇大台做唔到野係唔係問題？"},{"pid":"5daab928dd1705085fb07b935591bb6e4a9b0e95","tid":2241034,"uid":345502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"58fbc208b4eab3c17afeab54a14ac58a5cada614","tid":2241034,"uid":333488,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T05:28:09.000Z","msg":"你想下64咁多人死出軍隊，但之後嘅所謂制裁你睇下中共驚唔驚？ 李鵬，袁木享受到九十幾歲先至死，有冇後果？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:28:30.000Z","msg":"落左地獄你唔知啫<br />\n<br />\nsorry 按錯負評."},{"pid":"9ab1621fe1f1bbf7d170e372333df0763059edb3","tid":2241034,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T07:28:59.000Z","msg":"拜登上台<br />\n已經乜撚國際線都收晒皮啦<br />\n以我理解<br />\n中國已經係正接稱霸"},{"pid":"144f7c03d6baa6d07d60ee085db230f8d8fce32a","tid":2241034,"uid":13745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid"